title: (Weds Part 2) Did Amy Get Scammed at the Gas Station? + Amy Reviews Back to the Future After Watching for the 1st Time!
itunes:title: (Weds Part 2) Did Amy Get Scammed at the Gas Station? + Amy Reviews Back to the Future After Watching for the 1st Time!
description:
Amy reveals what happened to her yesterday at the gas station and wants to ask us if she thinks she got scammed? Morgan2 was given the assignment by Bobby to watch Back to the Future for the first time. Does a movie from the 80’s hold up to today?
